<h1>About PSST!</h1>

    <p>Psst is a new, exciting, messaging service like nothing you've seen before!</p>

    <p>PSST is a micro-blogging service that allows users to post short messages (Pssts)
    of 150 characters or less.  All messages are public but a user can follow any other user
    and get their Pssts included in their home pages.  Each user has a page that lists only
    their own Pssts, there is also a page that lists mentions of a user (@ + username).</p>

